title: Wendie Malick / Arthritis
description: Sean faces the music over his tendonitis from playing the piano and delves deeply into stress over his upcoming colonoscopy. Wendie Malick talks about managing her arthritis and breaking her ankle motorcycling in Africa.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
